He handled Tyrant like a pro.[BR]
If anyone is up to the task, I[BR]
think it's him.[BR]
He's my servant now.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
[SizeWave][Size 24]Heeheeheehahaha!
[Wait][End]
}

#message:0E:119
{
[Style Right]
Wow! You're full of confidence[BR]
today, my lady![BR]
[Pause 8]I sa-Boo-te you!
[Wait][End]
}

#message:0E:11A
{
