#message:0E:11E
{
[Style Narrate]
[InputOff]The Sass Key has joined the party!![BR]
[InputOn][Wait][Next]
Press [C-UP] to sass out the surrounding[BR]
enemies and leave them confused.[BR]
And yes, I did say [C-UP].[BR]
[Wait][Next]
You see, the game was getting kind of[BR]
boring and we needed to innovate, so[BR]
let's make the player press a slightly[BR]
different input.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
If you're tired of life, just press[BR]
[C-LEFT] and the Sass Key will yell a bunch[BR]
of slurs and call your mum fat.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
He really is the most overpowered[BR]
partner in the game.[BR]
I sure hope you don't lose him.[Wait][End]
}

#message:0E:11F
{
[Style Narrate]
[InputOff]The Sass Key has left the party...[BR]
[InputOn][Wait][Next]
Dang! Well you'll never believe this, but[BR]
the Sass Key is no longer on the team.[BR]
[Pause 5]Bro thought he was on the team.[BR]
Well he was! And now he's gone![BR]
[Wait][Next]
I think that means that the next[BR]
boss is going to be really hard.[BR]
[Pause 10]Only way to win might be to use the[BR]
Endeavor and Quick Attack combo.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
But you're not a rat.[BR]
You're Mario.[Wait][End]
}

